headline.main: Late Shots Carry No. 6 Oregon State Past No. 15 UCLA 63-53
headline.print_headline: Late Shots Carry No. 6 Oregon State Past No. 15 UCLA 63-53

lead_paragraph: Quiet on the scoresheet the entire second half, Sydney Wiese finally found a bit of space as the final minutes ticked away.
